{"id": 2519, "genre": 1000, "title": "线上跟人聊天，你都有遵循哪些“礼尚往来”的原则？", "description": "聊天时我打两排文字，而你回我两秒语音，你是不是看不起我？（图片来自：iStock ©️ Retrorocket）", "record_count": 14755, "comment_count": 34, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180913211724t94s5UryqgIlE8ew.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-09-17T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4672, "title": "线上跟人聊天，你都有遵循哪些“礼尚往来”的原则？", "content": "你在线上聊天时都遵循着哪些不成文的原则？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 298432, "content": "对方发语音，跟着改成发语音回复，反之亦然", "image": "img/option/option/20180913213057Pf9FbJLd2cMCjKo8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298433, "content": "如果对方总是很久才回复，能秒回也要等上一会再回", "image": "img/option/option/201809132145204yc9lMjGWJ80YzvP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298434, "content": "我讲正事对方连续用表情包回应，最后总会演变成斗图", "image": "img/option/option/20180913214554FmCeyR0GznoSBH7i.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298435, "content": "没打招呼就打来的视频／语音，先挂掉发文字问咋了", "image": "img/option/option/20180913214503XfpWNSGwMBI3KJcY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298453, "content": "“哈喽，在吗？”之后没下文了，直接发个问号回复", "image": "img/option/option/20180913214444whc7p3WqoavjUAt9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298479, "content": "经常点赞捧场的人，平时也会顺手点赞 ta 发的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20180913221623DfHOKsQ48k37uXWY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298502, "content": "聚会后被好友@并发了合照，也会发一条状态来回应", "image": "img/option/option/20180913232646gxcYPrDNndZaJ98G.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 298691, "content": "经常转发或@我的人，看到有趣内容时也会先给 ta 看", "image": "img/option/option/20180913232630ayS6RE8tcrQvzwnK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}